行，或不會續約。他表示，對上一次執行「bottom」制是樓市上一次跌市2015年。<br />\n<br />\n本港另一間龍頭代理行中原地產，本月更要蝕入肉。據知，中原住宅部截至本月29日佣金收入僅1.1億元，與公司每月保本線2.5億元比較，全月恐勁蝕逾1億元。中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑日前表示，公司本月業績有機會是自今年2月以來首次「見紅」。<br />\n<br />\n今年首十個月，中原地產有500名前線代理佣金收入不足10萬元，佔公司前線代理約一成人手，當中200人更「食白果」，於1至6月未能開單成交，全數至今亦是零成交，公司現時已發出嚴重警告信。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"租約到期分行，要求業主減租 &lt;- 廢淡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"支持業主加租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad31c8b54a5e433aed4591da9bafc8044e77e9cc","tid":882619,"uid":59746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"低置區應該多返d 人吹水啦"},{"pid":"2ab1c883846fa8f22a9e7feef9f17c037253cf07","tid":882619,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bce5b1bd1c05b5872bd9d6ece2b8f14eb5a856d","tid":882619,"uid":97,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"連登低智post 班aa點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"所以咪咁得閒上連登屌柒我地呢班廢淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e1c2ce911f6052901996fa7677c1dc3ea919c9","tid":882619,"uid":188176,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"地產狗本身都已經係人形垃圾<br />\n仲要係地產狗最垃圾個10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對香港簡直係災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86976720723d320a606a9278992bcb6b6f49a032","tid":882619,"uid":216780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"哇睇嚟今次真係樓爆"},{"pid":"7c4ed0e0e0131ce3015820a86bf9